  "details": "\n---\n_-= Per source details. Do not edit below this line.=-_\n\n## Source: kam193 (2098233a75602dd1779f720f566420f4a88ec77694b206e7858323b5aeea38d5)\nPackage is disguised as a utility, but in fact loads encrypted code as modules. However, loading it requires knowing the decryption key which is not included in the package.\n\n\n---\n\nCategory: MALICIOUS - The campaign has clearly malicious intent, like infostealers.\n\n\nCampaign: 2026-05-ggfmttygl\n\n\nReasons (based on the campaign):\n\n\n - obfuscation\n\n\n - The malicious code is intentionally included in a dependency of the package\n",
